About.Name: Dennis Vickers
About.AboutText: My name is Dennis Vickers, I'm a Computer Science Professor based in Seattle, WA. I have developed many types of applications from complex modelling tools to Ecommerce platforms. I'm passionate about cutting-edge, pixel-perfect, beautiful interfaces and intuitively implemented UX.
